Allen School of Computer Science & Engineering University of Washington Seattle, WA, 98195-2355 mushr@cs.washington.edu https://mushr.io Abstract ‚ÄîWe present MuSHR, the Multi-agent System for non-Holonomic Racing.
MuSHR can be built for $600, through the use of off-the-shelf components, and user-friendly build instructions, found at our website, (https://mushr.io).
A complete open-source software stack can be found at our Github pages, ((https://github.com/prl-mushr)).
